== 發展 ==

名稱「Sol Trigger」於2011年11月在日本地區首次註冊<ref name="nextrpg">{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2011/11/09/is-sol-trigger-imageepochs-next-self-published-rpg/|title=Is Sol Trigger Imageepoch’s Next Self Published RPG?|author=Spencer|publisher=SiliconEra|accessdate=2012-07-14|archive-date=2018-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181026223440/http://www.siliconera.com/2011/11/09/is-sol-trigger-imageepochs-next-self-published-rpg/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而遊戲則是在2012年5月公布，並在[[Fami通|Fami通]]發問<ref name="blasting">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/sol-trigger-blasting-this-august-in-japan-6375662|title=Sol Trigger blasting this August in Japan|publisher=GameSpot|first=Jonathan|last=Toyad|accessdate=2012-07-14|archive-date=2012-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025035758/http://www.gamespot.com/news/sol-trigger-blasting-this-august-in-japan-6375662|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有人曾透露這可能是公司嘗試過的高預算產品<ref name="blasting" />，但卻是在[[PlayStation_Portable|PlayStation Portable]]上的最後一個遊戲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://andriasang.com/con11q/psp_date_changes/|title=Imageepoch's Sol Trigger Delayed, Acquire Akiba's Trip Plus Pushed Up|publisher=Andriasang|first=Anoop|last=Gantayat|accessdate=2012-07-14|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130506164323/http://andriasang.com/con11q/psp_date_changes/|archivedate=2013-05-06|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。工作人員包括曾我部修司為角色設計師，是曾作《[[女神異聞錄4|女神異聞錄4]]》漫畫，遊戲劇本作家野島一成，曾寫過部分《[[最终幻想VII|最终幻想VII]]》、《[[王國之心|王國之心]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/5891187/this-new-japanese-rpg-has-soul|title=This New Japanese RPG Has Soul|first=Brian|last=Ashcraft|publisher=Kotaku|accessdate=2012-07-14|archive-date=2016-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160824062557/http://kotaku.com/5891187/this-new-japanese-rpg-has-soul|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而CG影片的部分是由JCSTAFF負責<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2012-07-05/sol-trigger-psp-game-story-cyril-videos-posted|title=Sol Trigger PSP Game's Story, Cyril Videos Posted|publisher=Anime News Network|accessdate=2012-07-14|archive-date=2016-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161029013846/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2012-07-05/sol-trigger-psp-game-story-cyril-videos-posted|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

原定於2012年8月30日發售，但後來要求零售商推遲到10月4日推出，因當時有太多遊戲在日本該天發布<ref name="september">{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2012/05/17/you-can-try-sol-trigger-in-july-but-cant-buy-it-until-september/|title=You Can Try Sol Trigger In July, But Can't Buy It Until September|author=Spencer|publisher=SiliconEra|accessdate=2012-07|archive-date=2016-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160506212953/http://www.siliconera.com/2012/05/17/you-can-try-sol-trigger-in-july-but-cant-buy-it-until-september/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。推出後，在2012年7月在日本[[PlayStation_Store|PlayStation Store]]上下載<ref name="september" />。

為了促使遊戲發行，在[[網頁瀏覽器|網頁瀏覽器]]上推出一個小遊戲《Sol Trigger Training School》，是一格鬥遊戲，玩家可快點擊鼠標，能收到Sol Trigger的獎金密碼解鎖<ref>{{cite web |author=By Spencer . October 1, 2012 . 12:30am |url=http://www.siliconera.com/2012/10/01/sol-trigger-one-on-one-fighting-game-unlocks-weapons-for-psp-rpg/ |title=Sol Trigger One-On-One Fighting Game Unlocks Weapons For PSP RPG |publisher=Siliconera |date=2012-10-01 |accessdate=2013-06-01 |archive-date=2016-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160506205939/http://www.siliconera.com/2012/10/01/sol-trigger-one-on-one-fighting-game-unlocks-weapons-for-psp-rpg/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 銷售與續作 ==

截至10月中旬，該遊戲已在日本售出52,234份<ref name="siliconera1">{{cite web |author=By Spencer . October 19, 2012 . 2:38am |url=http://www.siliconera.com/2012/10/19/imageepoch-ceo-interested-in-making-sol-trigger-sequel-perhaps-for-vita/ |title=Imageepoch CEO Interested In Making Sol Trigger Sequel, Perhaps For Vita |publisher=Siliconera |date=2012-10-19 |accessdate=2013-06-01 |archive-date=2019-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191104072638/https://www.siliconera.com/2012/10/19/imageepoch-ceo-interested-in-making-sol-trigger-sequel-perhaps-for-vita/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Ryoei Mikage、公司創始人[[首席執行官|首席執行官]]表示，有感興趣對本作推出續作的可能<ref name="siliconera1" />。「Cyril」在另一個Imageepoch遊戲中作為一個可玩的人物，《騎士年代記戰略》發揮著本作的特性之一<ref>{{cite web |author=By Spencer . October 4, 2012 . 5:15pm |url=http://www.siliconera.com/2012/10/04/sol-trigger-character-maces-her-way-into-another-imaggepoch-game/ |title=Sol Trigger Character Maces Her Way Into Another Imaggepoch Game |publisher=Siliconera |date=2012-10-04 |accessdate=2013-06-01 |archive-date=2019-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031210404/https://www.siliconera.com/2012/10/04/sol-trigger-character-maces-her-way-into-another-imaggepoch-game/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

